{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Education Maintenance Allowance (EMA)"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/education-maintenance-allowance-ema.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/education-maintenance-allowance-ema"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"1735","business_proposition":false,"alternative_title":"","overview":"You can still apply for Education Maintenance Allowance (EMA) if you're studying in Northern Ireland, Scotland or Wales. Students in England may be able to get a 16 to 19 Bursary Fund","updated_at":"2012-10-08T17:07:05+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You may be able to claim Education Maintenance Allowance (<abbr title=\"Education Maintenance Allowance\">EMA</abbr>) if you\u2019re studying in Northern Ireland, Scotland or Wales. <abbr title=\"Education Maintenance Allowance\">EMA</abbr> is now closed in England.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You can apply for: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.delni.gov.uk/index/further-and-higher-education/further-education/fe-financial-help/ema-educational-maintenance-allowance\" title=\"EMA in Northern Ireland\"><abbr title=\"Education Maintenance Allowance\">EMA</abbr> in Northern Ireland</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.emascotland.com/\" title=\"EMA in Scotland\"><abbr title=\"Education Maintenance Allowance\">EMA</abbr> in Scotland</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.studentfinancewales.co.uk/portal/page?_pageid=616,6382785&amp;_dad=portal&amp;_schema=PORTAL\" title=\"EMA in Wales\"><abbr title=\"Education Maintenance Allowance\">EMA</abbr> in Wales</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>If you&rsquo;re studying in England, you may be able to get a <a href=\"/1619-bursary-fund\" title=\"16-19 Bursary Fund\">16-19 Bursary Fund</a> to help with your studying costs.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>To find out more about the closure of <abbr title=\"Education Maintenance Allowance\">EMA</abbr>, call the Learner Support helpline on: 0800 121 8989</p>\n</div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Student finance and loans","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/education%2Fstudent-finance.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Including loans, bursaries, grants, student finance and paying back loans","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=education%2Fstudent-finance","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/education/student-finance"},"parent":{"title":"Education","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/education.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Get help if you&#39;re at school, planning to go on to further or higher education, looking for training or interested in a student or career development loan.","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=education","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/education"},"parent":null}}]],["related",[{"title":"16 - 19 Bursary Fund","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/1619-bursary-fund.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/1619-bursary-fund","format":"answer","details":{"need_id":"1882","business_proposition":false}}]]],"parts":null}